<CSSBorder-inline-color>
<summary>
The <strong><c>border-inline-color</c></strong> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</see> property defines the color of the logical inline borders of an element, which maps to a physical border color depending on the element's writing mode, directionality, and text orientation. It corresponds to the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-color">border-top-color</see> and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-color">border-bottom-color</see>, or <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-color">border-right-color</see> and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-color">border-left-color</see> property depending on the values defined for <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode">writing-mode</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction">direction</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-orientation">text-orientation</see>.
</summary>
<remarks>
<para>EmbedInteractiveExample("pages/css/border-inline-color.html")</para><para>The border color in the other dimension can be set with <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-block-color">border-block-color</see> which sets <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-block-start-color">border-block-start-color</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-block-end-color">border-block-end-color</see>.</para>
<para>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_logical_properties_and_values">CSS Logical Properties and Values</see><br/>-This property maps to the physical border properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-color">border-top-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-color">border-right-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-color">border-bottom-color</see>, or <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-color">border-left-color</see>.<br/>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode">writing-mode</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction">direction</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-orientation">text-orientation</see><br/></para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-inline-color"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
</CSSBorder-inline-color>
